# Copy to .env (gitignored). ONLY needed for the OPTIONAL corpus rebuild
# (src/census_harvest.py, src/harvest_pool.py fetch the deposited replication data from
# Harvard Dataverse). Every paper number reproduces from the committed artifacts with
# NO .env, NO key, and NO network: just run `python reproduce.py`.
#
# Dataverse installation to harvest from (default: https://dataverse.harvard.edu):
DATAVERSE_SERVER=
# API key (optional; the census datasets are public and download without one):
DATAVERSE_API_KEY=
